short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Place orders on Robinhood via TradingView alerts

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: This extension allows you to connect your Robinhood Brokerage account to TradingView so you can make trades right from your TradingView charts. Also, it allows you to create alerts based off of your strategy and will automatically place trades on Robinhood for you when your criteria is met. If you have a trading strategy that you want to automate, this extension does the trading for you!
